      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should call the doctor but the clinic is closed until tomorrow and i can barely sleep or even function right now. i've read online that people take it all the time in the second and third trimester without issues. can u just tell me if it's generally considered safe or if there's like a standard dose that most people use? i just need to know if it's a major risk or not.",
